ArcelorMittal S.A. Says Letter Declaring Force Majeure Issued

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-08-12T15:36:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/arcelormittal-south-africa-says-it-issued-letter-declaring-force-majeure.html
ArcelorMittal (MT)  South Africa Ltd. said
a letter declaring force majeure was issued to customers
yesterday as it estimates it could lose around 400,000 metric
tons of steel because of a structural failure at its gas
cleaning plant in Newcastle.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  